divs: Sighting Details I was taking pictures of the moon and venus, the sky was very clear, my surprise was when I saw the picture on the camera. Appears a big blue objet in the picture. I took 4 pictures and the object appears in two with different position. The area is full of chemical plants.
Summary: A blue object appears in a picture.
